=== 評論招待會 ===
評論家對小說進行了評價，評論總匯{{le|書纖|Literary Hub#Book Marks}}於9條評論中，報告有一個正面及兩個混合評論<ref name=BookMarks>{{cite web|url=https://bookmarks.reviews/reviews/midnight-sun-2/|title=Book Marks reviews of ''Midnight Sun'' by Stephenie Meyer|website=Book Marks|access-date=10 September 2020|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208101226/https://bookmarks.reviews/reviews/midnight-sun-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[衛報|衛報]]》的埃勒·亨特（Elle Hunt）寫道，這本書被「長期覆蓋」且編輯不足。她為了如何嚴格遵守原始《暮光之城》的場景和缺乏新的絕殺使得這本書乏味而感到感嘆<ref>{{cite news |last1=Hunt |first1=Elle |title=Midnight Sun by Stephenie Meyer review – dusk falls on Twilight saga |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2020/aug/07/midnight-sun-stephenie-meyer-review-twilight |access-date=26 August 2020 |work=The Guardian |date=7 August 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203023705/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2020/aug/07/midnight-sun-stephenie-meyer-review-twilight |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在《[[獨立報|獨立報]]》的安妮·洛德（Annie Lord）還注意到這跟《暮光之城》有很多重疊的地方，並稱該作品為「可笑的不好」，但她指出書迷會喜歡有關愛德華與他妹妹關係的新見解<ref>{{cite news |last1=Lord |first1=Annie |title=Midnight Sun review: Time’s up for Twilight’s twisted romance |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/reviews/midnight-sun-review-twilight-saga-stephenie-meyer-bella-edward-a9658561.html |work=The Independent |date=6 August 2020 |language=en |accessdate=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2020-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119205353/https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/books/reviews/midnight-sun-review-twilight-saga-stephenie-meyer-bella-edward-a9658561.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{le|柯庫斯評論|Kirkus Reviews}}認為這本書的「冰川速度」使人們可以專注於刻畫，並預測粉絲會原諒甚至喜歡它的「過度與放縱」。在《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》中，卡琳·填納汴（Karin Tanabe）批評角色缺乏多樣性，形容奎魯特一眾角色為「典型的B列表角色」。她還指出，男女主角之間的性張力因必須堅持原始故事情節而受到阻礙<ref>{{cite news |last1=Tanabe |first1=Karin |title='Midnight Sun’ gives ‘Twilight’ fans a new story to sink their teeth into — sort of |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/books/midnight-sun-gives-twilight-fans-a-new-story-to-sink-their-teeth-into--sort-of/2020/08/08/2dca2642-d9a2-11ea-9c3b-dfc394c03988_story.html |work=Washington Post |date=9 August 2020 |language=en |accessdate=2021-02-15 |archive-date=2020-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228233458/https://www.washingtonpost.com/entertainment/books/midnight-sun-gives-twilight-fans-a-new-story-to-sink-their-teeth-into--sort-of/2020/08/08/2dca2642-d9a2-11ea-9c3b-dfc394c03988_story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

